{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/1oi5wn","slide":1,"text":"India's energy supply chain does not fail because leaders lack dashboards. It fails when a moving disruption turns into a late, opaque decision. PetraVigil is built for that exact moment: it turns one source-labelled signal into a reviewable procurement decision, with the analyst still in control. This is not an AI that buys crude. It is decision intelligence that shows its work.\n\nTransition: Why does this matter enough to act now? Because India’s exposure is structural, not theoretical."}
