{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/9m71ia","slide":3,"text":"Most risk products stop at an alert, and most generic supply tools treat oil as interchangeable. But a decision is only useful if it respects the refinery’s compatible crude grades, alternative-route capacity, corridor exposure, and a named human approver. PetraVigil makes those constraints part of the product—not a spreadsheet after the fact.\n\nTransition: That insight leads to a very different kind of workflow."}
